summary: This is a texture mood that adds Bluish White Tengwar inscription to the daedric sword/greatsword/dagger. It is similar to my red glow tengwar mod.
descriptionHtml:
This is a texture mood that adds Tengwar inscription to the daedric sword/greatsword/dagger. It is similar to my red glow tengwar mod.

If u like it please ENDORSE guys!! it\'d be appreciated immensely! thanks :)

Installation:

Extract contents (Data folder)and place it in ur skyrim folder.

My other mod:

Tengwar Inscription Red glow - http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=5236
